  id: wfo_sftdc_02
  displayName: School Target
  description: 'The army claims the enemy is positioned inside a civilian school
    building and wants to strike it.

    If executed, the offensive could accelerate
    military progress.

    However, the risk of civilian casualties and international
    backlash is high.

    They request your media support to justify and shape public
    perception of the operation.'
  devNote: "feed skilleri olu\u015Fturuldu\u011Funda eklenecek"
  eventNote: "ordu ilerlemesi i\xE7in \xF6nemli oldu\u011Funu d\xFC\u015F\xFCnerek
    birka\xE7 tane okul vurmay\u0131 ister\nsenden de istedi\u011Fi bu operasyonun
    alg\u0131 aya\u011F\u0131n\u0131 \xFCstlenmen\nkabul edip medyada alg\u0131 pompalayarak
    operasyonu me\u015Frula\u015Ft\u0131rmaya \xE7al\u0131\u015Fabilirsin, itibar\u0131n
    d\xFC\u015Fer ancak war supportun ciddi oranda artar\nreddedebilirsin, itibar\u0131n
    artar, siyasi n\xFCfuzun biraz azal\u0131r, war supportun d\xFC\u015Fer. ayr\u0131ca
    kabul etmek protest tetiklenme ihtimalini de \xF6n\xFCm\xFCzdeki 2 event d\xF6nemi
    i\xE7in ge\xE7ici olarak artt\u0131r\u0131r"
